(797, 39, 'E-00712', '', 17, 'Gucci Guilty Elixir de Parfum Pour Femme, 60ml', '649517738-9683198b634034ce8b37c3cd3ed45b6b-photo_2025-10-30_22-37-39.jpg', 187, '$', 100, 'Gucci Guilty Elixir de Parfum Pour Femme is a powerful invitation to love and self-acceptance. The fragrance has an ambery floral scent that pulses with refreshing energy and charm, enhancing the signature notes of Gucci Guilty. The bouquet is presented in a brightly colored flacon, created to mirror its man&#039;s counterpart in their sleek symmetry.', 'à¸ªà¹ˆà¸‡à¸Ÿà¸£à¸µ', 0, '2025-10-30 14:38:34'),
