(801, 39, 'E-00716', '', 17, '3 Ch&acirc;tain, Crayon D&eacute;finition Sourcils Eyebrow Pencil', '379431587-46c04358035c446d6666d046c6813505-photo_2025-10-30_22-45-57.jpg', 33, '$', 100, 'A versatile tool for drawing and filling in eyebrows, Crayon D&eacute;finition Sourcils delivers the experience of a light, luxurious powder within a pencil. The innovative texture provides flake-free matte color in a buildable and customizable finish, offering ultimate control in filling and defining brows with precision. A blendable formula emulates real hair to create a naturally defined look while the dual-sided construction features a brush at the end, for combing the color through for a polished finish.', 'à¸ªà¹ˆà¸‡à¸Ÿà¸£à¸µ', 0, '2025-10-30 14:46:35'),
(802, 39, 'E-00717', '', 17, 'Gucci Brume De Beaut&eacute;, Beauty Mist', '633193346-c689fb72f9239785c942d2287b21ff18-photo_2025-10-30_22-47-43.jpg', 81, '$', 100, 'Brume De Beaut&eacute; is a hybrid product formulated with soothing and protective ingredients, as well as hydrating properties of up to 48 hours. Helping to shield skin from pollution, it can be used to hydrate the face for a glowing skin finish &ndash; before, during, or post makeup wear. Black Rose Oil provides soothing and antioxidant properties, Hyaluronic Acid ensures hydration and a healthy-looking glow of skin, while a blend of film-former actives helps set makeup. From preparing the skin to perfecting and maintaining a fresh face throughout the day, Brume De Beaut&eacute; is a multi-use beauty fix for all needs.', 'à¸ªà¹ˆà¸‡à¸Ÿà¸£à¸µ', 0, '2025-10-30 14:48:38'),
(803, 39, 'E-00718', '', 17, 'Multi-use Palette De Beaut&eacute; Quatuor, Summerina Brown', '201120448-7a30adbe04aecb0053ac1d711c3cc094-photo_2025-10-30_22-49-21.jpg', 70, '$', 100, 'Palette de Beaut&eacute; Quatuor multiplies creative freedom with a four-part palette for eyes, lips, and cheeks. From soft to sophisticated and every look in between, intuitive formulas and inventive shades offer endless combinations. Comfortable to wear and long-lasting, three powder formulas in satin and matte finishes can be used as eyeshadow or blush. These colors are combined with a cream formula, ideated to warm up eyes, lips, and cheeks. Inspired by Gucci Beauty lipsticks, the allover cream shade brings a bare-to-bold blushing effect that intensifies with every touch.', 'à¸ªà¹ˆà¸‡à¸Ÿà¸£à¸µ', 0, '2025-10-30 14:50:26'),
